<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70A7214A12" svcinfotypenbr = "06" svcinfoqualnbr = "03">
<title>
During compressor operation, a rumbling noise is heard as to engine speed increases
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A7214004001">
<title>
Abnormal Noise from Compressor
</title>
<diag type = "condition">
<condition>
<ptxt>
During compressor operation, a rumbling noise is heard as to engine speed increases
</ptxt>
</condition>
<ps>
<ptxt>
Inadequate clearance in scroll area
</ptxt>
</ps>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace compressor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A7216038"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
</diag>
